  "translations": {
    "en": "Muhammad b. Ahmad b. Ali b. Asad al-Asadi narrated to us in Ray in Rajab in the year 347 AH. He said: Muhammad b. Abi Ayyub narrated to me. He said: Ja’far b. Sunaid b. Dawud narrated to us. He said: My father narrated to me. He said: Yusuf b. Muhammad b. al-Munkadir narrated to us from his father, from Jabir b. Abdullah. He said: The Messenger of Allah (peace be upon him and his family) said:",
    "ur": "ہم سے محمد بن احمد بن علی بن اسد اسدی نے ری میں رجب ۳۴۷ ہجری میں بیان کیا:",
    "tr": "Muhammed b. Ahmed b. Ali b. Esed el-Esedî bize Rey'de 347 yılı Receb ayında rivayet etti. Dedi ki: ... Resûlullah (s.a.v.s.) buyurdu:",
    "fa": "محمد بن احمد بن علی بن اسد اسدی در ری در ماه رجب سال ۳۴۷ برای ما روایت کرد. ... رسول خدا صلی الله علیه وآله فرمود:",
    "id": "Muhammad bin Ahmad bin Ali bin Asad al-Asadi menceritakan kepada kami di Ray pada bulan Rajab tahun 347 H. ... Rasulullah (s.a.w.s.) bersabda:",
    "bn": "মুহাম্মাদ ইবনে আহমাদ ... রাসূলুল্লাহ (সা.) বলেছেন:",
    "es": "Muhammad b. Ahmad b. Ali b. Asad al-Asadi nos narró en Ray en Rajab del año 347 H. ... El Mensajero de Dios (s.a.w.s.) dijo:",
    "fr": "Muhammad b. Ahmad b. Ali b. Asad al-Asadi nous a rapporté à Ray en Rajab de l’an 347 H. ... Le Messager de Dieu (s.a.w.s.) a dit :",
    "de": "Muhammad b. Ahmad b. Ali b. Asad al-Asadi berichtete uns in Ray im Radschab 347 n. H. ... Der Gesandte Gottes (s.a.w.s.) sprach:",
    "ru": "Мухаммад ибн Ахмад ... Посланник Аллаха (с.а.в.с.) сказал:",
    "zh": "穆罕默德·本·艾哈迈德……安拉的使者（愿主福安之）说："
